OL,3,CManchester Arena bomb survivors to
OL,4,Cfind out whether harassment claim
OL,5,Csuccessful
OL,7,FTwo survivors of the Manchester Arena
OL,8,Fbombing are due to find out whether
OL,9,Fthey have won a High Court harassment
OL,10,Fcase against a former television
OL,11,Fproducer who believes the attack was
OL,12,Fstaged.
OL,14,FMartin Hibbert and his daughter Eve
OL,15,Fare suing former television producer
OL,16,FRichard Hall for harassment and data
OL,17,Fprotection over his claims in several
OL,18,Fvideos and a book that the attack was
OL,19,Fstaged.
