OL,4,Cfind out whether harassment claim
OL,5,Csuccessful
OL,7,FThe father and daughter were at the
OL,8,FAriana Grande concert in May 2017 and
OL,9,Fsuffered life-changing injuries, with
OL,10,FMr Hibbert left with a spinal cord
OL,11,Finjury and Miss Hibbert facing severe
OL,12,Fbrain damage.
OL,14,FBut Mr Hall has claimed his actions `
OL,15,Fincluding an incident of filming Miss
OL,16,FHibbert outside her home ` were in the
OL,17,Fpublic interest as a journalist and
OL,18,Fthat "millions of people have bought a
OL,19,Flie" about the attack.
