OL,7,FHe told the London court in a three-
OL,8,Fand-a-half-day trial in July: "The
OL,9,Fprimary evidence shows there was no
OL,10,Fbomb in that room that exploded."
OL,12,FMrs Justice Steyn is now due to give
OL,13,Fher decision on the case in writing on
OL,14,FWednesday, 23 October.
