OL,3,CManchester Arena bomb survivors to
OL,4,Cfind out whether harassment claim
OL,5,Csuccessful
OL,7,FSalman Abedi killed 22 people and
OL,8,Finjured hundreds when he detonated the
OL,9,Fhomemade rucksack-bomb in the crowd of
OL,10,Fconcert-goers, with the court told
OL,11,Fthat the Hibberts were some of the
OL,12,Fnearest people to him at the time of
OL,13,Fthe blast.
OL,15,FMr Hall has claimed that several of
OL,16,Fthose who died are living abroad or
OL,17,Fwere dead before the attack, telling
OL,18,Fthe court he believed that no-one was
OL,19,F"genuinely injured" in the bombing.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@SO]
