OL,5,Csuccessful
OL,7,FBut Jonathan Price, for the Hibberts,
OL,8,Fsaid the pair were some of the closest
OL,9,Fto Abedi when he detonated the bomb
OL,10,Fand that the attack changed Mr
OL,11,FHibbert's life "in every conceivable
OL,12,Fway".
OL,14,F"They have both suffered life-changing
OL,15,Finjuries from which they will never
OL,16,Frecover," the barrister said.
