OL,4,Cfind out whether harassment claim
OL,5,Csuccessful
OL,7,FThe court heard that Mr Hibbert
OL,8,Freceived 22 wounds from shrapnel, and
OL,9,FMiss Hibbert suffered a "catastrophic
OL,10,Fbrain injury" after a bolt from the
OL,11,Fbomb struck her in the head ` leading
OL,12,Fto her being presumed dead at the
OL,13,Fscene.
OL,15,FMr Price added: "Martin, paralysed,
OL,16,Fsaw Eve lying next to him with a hole
OL,17,Fin her head and assumed he was
OL,18,Fwatching her die, unable to help. He
OL,19,Fsaw others lying dead or injured
OL,20,Faround him."
